inputs.description: A collection of arguments for invoking getDelegatedAdministrators.

servicePrincipal.description: Specifies a service principal name. If specified, then the operation lists the delegated administrators only for the specified service. If you don't specify a service principal, the operation lists all delegated administrators for all services in your organization.

outputs.description: A collection of values returned by getDelegatedAdministrators.

delegatedAdministrators.description: The list of delegated administrators in your organization, which have the following attributes:

id.description: The provider-assigned unique ID for this managed resource.
